NID 6 is 'NotoSerifMyanmar-SemiCondensedExtraLight', Everything looks good.

MS NID 16/17

Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Noto Serif Myanmar SemiCondensed ExtraLight' ≠ 'Noto Serif Myanmar SemCond ExtLt' (NID 1).

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Noto Serif Myanmar SemiCondensed Light' ≠ 'Noto Serif Myanmar SemCond Light' (NID 1).

Noto Serif Myanmar SemCond Regular (NotoSerifMyanmar-SemiCondensed.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Noto Serif Myanmar SemiCondensed' ≠ 'Noto Serif Myanmar SemCond' (NID 1).

Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Noto Serif Myanmar SemiCondensed Medium' ≠ 'Noto Serif Myanmar SemCond Med' (NID 1).

NID 6 is 'NotoSerifMyanmar-SemiCondensedSemiBold', Everything looks good.
